{
  "stem": "4187.2",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So it was my mother and us three girls, so that's four of us.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And one other person, an older person from-- from our hometown happened to be.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So my mother had her-- her medicine bag with her.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "She carried that.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That is the only thing that we had with us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And she carried that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And a German came by and-- and said, immediately, you know, what's that?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And my mother said, you know, it's my medicine bag.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And [INAUDIBLE] he said, you know, doctor?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And said, come with me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So he took my mother, immediately.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And that was it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We didn't know where, how.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "That was it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "My mother disappeared.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So there we were, my sisters, myself, and that one other woman.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And then, as were only four of us then, another person from my hometown stepped back into our line.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Now, she happened to be the wife of a-- a professor, who my mother worked with.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "So at least, this was a-- because she was an older woman.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I don't know how old she would have been, but to me, she looked ancient.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "She was probably all of 50, if that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Yeah, it would have been about that, because my mother was 44.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "But, you know, to me, she was ancient.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And-- but at least it was someone we knew, so that was good.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And so there was [?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Jocka, ?] my older sister, [?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Suzy, ?] my young sister, and then-- then myself.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And on both sides, were two other women.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Now, in the center, opposite, was a table.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And there sat an SS man, who was, of course, Mengele.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And people were walking up to him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And whatever was being said, we didn't know.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
